import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import {router} from './router'
import {store} from './store/store'
import VueResource from 'vue-resource'

Vue.use(VueResource)


Vue.filter()


Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  render: h => h(App),
  router,
  store
}).$mount('#app')
